data.meta_description: Download this stock image: Jun 17, 2008 - Hollywood, California, USA - CYD CHARISSE, a former co-star of Fred Astaire and Gene Kelly, has died in Los Angeles aged 87, her publicist says. The actress-dancer from Texas died at Cedars-Sinai Medical Center after suffering an apparent heart attack on Monday.
